{"tid":978143,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[ART撚]有冇人對紋理/圖案/民族風有認識?","createTime":"2019-01-11T16:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T16:24:56.000Z","uid":227688,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d921adb637c500d132a82cfdd46445c1576b6ae9","tid":978143,"uid":227688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"小弟一直對紋理/圖案有興趣<br />\n一直覺得好多野加上呢種紋之後好鬼靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SYNkF0B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSYNkF0B.jpg&h=fc416030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但我一直都唔知呢類雕紋係ART邊飯 叫咩名 有咩分派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我想問下有冇人對呢種紋有認識?<br />\n可唔可以介紹下同講下正式名係咩 想研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/184jb7n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F184jb7n.jpg&h=c16a2740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T48PzkH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT48PzkH.jpg&h=03673949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YUndgy3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYUndgy3.jpg&h=8d5160d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLzrBy4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLzrBy4.jpg&h=073bda64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外想問下有冇人對民族風有認識?<br />\n都係想研究同埋認識<br />\n我見有好多都係常見圖案 係咪有特別意思?<br />\n圖我搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋想問邊度有呢幾類嘅衣服買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒撚少出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c585f6f12c34a80afb3d234731439566bacd2c","tid":978143,"uid":227688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T16:20:38.000Z","msg":"開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4c0c571d63cd6937e757af96f89197b664af9d","tid":978143,"uid":64131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"keyword: scroll / flourish"},{"pid":"7a70a9f3a7dd72fc60f20f4d30c438fed11fabbf","tid":978143,"uid":227688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b4c0c571d63cd6937e757af96f89197b664af9d","tid":978143,"uid":64131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"keyword: scroll / flourish"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"係啦係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絲打有冇認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e105600a43b54621ce730a408443bdd27809d19f","tid":978143,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:48:21.000Z","msg":"好想學，做呢啲既雕刻師傅好難搵<br />\n<br />\n卷草紋"},{"pid":"ab08b1b99270e4e57535b85fb57c33e4e7ec7965","tid":978143,"uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T20:07:51.000Z","msg":"google<br />\ncultural pattern<br />\nantiqie pattern<br />\nflourish carving"},{"pid":"5fbcc20531d4c522e939521551ef11acd5ddcc72","tid":978143,"uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T20:10:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.antiquepatternlibrary.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.antiquepatternlibrary.org&d=qx6SGytK11ti6wVBFdTZ3pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=73591e9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.antiquepatternlibrary.org</a><br />\n<br />\n資料量太多"},{"pid":"c4262b9c7db441ce933eb9fde3321953ca0f4cf1","tid":978143,"uid":227688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e105600a43b54621ce730a408443bdd27809d19f","tid":978143,"uid":41355,"like":